        "care_text": "<p>At every step, we've chosen care over speed. We work only with partners who honor fair treatment, skilled craftsmanship, and the dignity of labor. Every Kaahu piece is made to last - not just in construction, but in meaning. We design with permanence in mind: clean lines, considered details, no waste.</p>",
